FAQ
Why choose stainless steel decorative panels?

Stainless steel decorative panels offer durability, corrosion resistance, luxury appearance, and low maintenance.

Are decorative stainless steel sheets customizable?

Yes. Custom colors, textures, finishes, and sizes are available for different architectural projects.

Which stainless steel material is recommended?

304 stainless steel is commonly used for interior projects, while 316L is recommended for humid or coastal environments.

